      "message": "Where are all the processor identifiers from?  I think this IntelFam6KabylakeL \nclassification can be simplified looking at: \nhttps://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/processors/processor-numbers.html\n\n *-10*  --\u003e CML\n *-8*U* --\u003e WHL_U\n *-8*Y* --\u003e AML_Y\n *-7*U* --\u003e KBL_U\n *-7*Y* --\u003e KBL_Y\n\nwith a specific first step pre-filtering the KBL_U_R that is a silicon refresh\nand a bit of a weird stepping anyway.",
